{"tid":1442588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<拋磚>唔好屌勇武兄弟無目的行動，因為唔夠人討論行動綱領，做足夠既文宣同網上輿論工作","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:55:29.000Z","uid":55974,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab602b063e3cdf3b4624369bbe940844d6749de","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"自罷工後，除左分化外，有無人認真討論下一步行動做乜，唔好再比手足白白去送頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武行動越黎越激，但係同一個時，被拉既手足越黎越多，每個行動少幾十，先換到震撼既相或者video<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而問題係，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">根本無人去有組織咁搶輿論陣地幫手足解釋，咁義士衝黎做乜？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有目的既衝擊，好似立法會咁，無人係會反對，因為佢地知道，衝擊係對準政權，入到去都係五大訴求。但係係每次行動之前，例如係遊行，明明係大一兩個星期前已經知去邊，都無poster，在地宣傳講行動目標係做緊咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早係屯門大媽，上水反水貨，元朗反黑，好清晰，係有對個目的。先天上，屯門，上水同元朗既活動，係一講，當地屋民會明。但係其他地區，無一個明顯既主題，就更加需要講清楚做緊乜，點解係呢區做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅隧唔比收錢，點解呢？就算手足做完件事，都應該係有文宣幫手講點解咁做，如果唔係，真係淪為擾民，唔係抗爭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;拋磚一&gt;<br />\n每當有港人港地，呢一類藍絲post一出，就要有水泥隊貼翻岩既資訊出黎。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲fb page三部曲<br />\nReport 放錯誤資訊既page，同入去留言<br />\n比like自己友既post<br />\nReport犯fb 社群條例既藍絲，要佢地禁言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;拋磚二&gt;<br />\n之前既黃絲page有好多開始現形<br />\n以芒向報情況最為嚴重<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDgjZzR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDgjZzR.png&h=5ac6759b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZya6eS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZya6eS.png&h=f5330095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由之前反毓民到明顯轉風向，呢d pagd係更加需要處理。<br />\n<br />\n三部曲<br />\nStep 1 - 水泥隊<br />\n講事實，呢d page係有一d淺藍既人，唔好屌，講導理，將自己友既留言推上去，講翻點解要咁做<br />\n<br />\nStep 2 - Report 成個page<br />\n<br />\nStep 3 - Report 個別admin<br />\n通常呢d page會知個admin係咩人，搵佢地po過咩，就去report佢地，要不停禁佢地言，要佢地用鬼acc po野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;拋磚三&gt;<br />\n<br />\n記得記得<br />\n<br />\n行動前<br />\n造文宣，係當區派同宣傳<br />\n<br />\n行動後<br />\n幫手足係網上，同落去受影響地區解説<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff91f6506733062b067724f98de49e537ed87640","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f486e4b9df44dc264de2ad649b144ef5da2f3a8","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cfa583106da3df98c77d3fc3948af84bf52a1f29","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c09f45daa1e21418ff27ff660d6d8adcef72ac3a","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c8369f61f4e34af6af2a7505c00f5fde3cf5ba25","tid":1442588,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔 改不了吃屎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6f15b776c470a033e061741cd0bead33a62cfd4","tid":1442588,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"請用以下內容代替push/推：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n721元朗恐襲<span style=\"color: red;\">第22日</span><br />\n警黑合作 <br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n大家copy and paste pls<br />\n並每日自行更新第xx日"},{"pid":"e08c3888f9ddfdfa873c61d970bacdf14805fd9c","tid":1442588,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f15b776c470a033e061741cd0bead33a62cfd4","tid":1442588,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2